    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=company : {{ $json.Company }}\nLocatjion: {{ $json.Location }}",
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are a lead generation and business discovery AI agent.\n\nYour task is to find companies based on a given business type and location, and return structured data containing their names and website links.\n\n## INPUT\nYou will receive:\n- Company Type (e.g., \"web design agency\", \"real estate firm\", \"fitness center\")\n- Location (e.g., \"Mumbai\", \"Berlin\", \"New York\")\n\n## OBJECTIVE\nSearch the internet and identify relevant companies that match the given type within the specified location.\n\n## STRICT INSTRUCTIONS\n\n1. You MUST use available browsing/search tools to find real companies.\n2. Focus ONLY on companies that:\n   - Match the given company type\n   - Are located in the specified location (or clearly serve that area)\n\n3. For each company, extract:\n   - Company Name\n   - Official Website URL\n\n4. Prioritize:\n   - Official company websites (not directories)\n   - Active and legitimate businesses\n   - Companies with clear branding and services\n\n5. Avoid:\n   - Listing platforms (e.g., Justdial, Yelp, Clutch) unless needed for discovery\n   - Duplicate companies\n   - Broken or invalid websites\n\n6. If a company does NOT have a website:\n   - Skip it\n\n7. Collect at least 40 –50 companies (if available)\n\n## OUTPUT FORMAT (STRICT JSON)\n\n{\n  \"location\": \"\",\n  \"company_type\": \"\",\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"company_name\": \"\",\n      \"website\": \"\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n\n## ADDITIONAL RULES\n- Do NOT hallucinate companies or websites\n- Only return verifiable businesses\n- Keep output clean and structured\n- No explanations, only JSON"
        }
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
      "position": [
        528,
        -160
      ],
      "id": "791d090b-b554-410d-8b88-68438c7c5532",
      "name": "Companies list generator"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "  // Get raw output\nconst rawOutput = $json.output;\n\n// Clean markdown (```json ... ```)\nconst cleaned = rawOutput\n  .replace(/```json/g, \"\")\n  .replace(/```/g, \"\")\n  .trim();\n\nlet parsed;\n\ntry {\n  parsed = JSON.parse(cleaned);\n} catch (error) {\n  return [{ json: { error: \"Invalid JSON format\" } }];\n}\n\n// Ensure results exist\nif (!parsed.results || !Array.isArray(parsed.results)) {\n  return [{ json: { error: \"No results found\" } }];\n}\n\n// Map all companies\nreturn parsed.results.map(company => {\n  return {\n    json: {\n      company_name: company.company_name || null,\n      website: company.website || null\n    }\n  };\n});"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
