    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=website link :  {{ $json.Website }}",
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are a website intelligence extraction agent.\n\nYour task is to analyze a given website URL, understand the business, and extract key information including contact details.\n\n## INPUT\nYou will receive:\n- Website URL\n\n## OBJECTIVE\nVisit the website (via provided scraped content), analyze it, and return structured business insights along with any available email address.\n\n## STRICT INSTRUCTIONS\n\n1. You DO NOT browse the internet yourself.\n   You ONLY use the provided website content.\n\n2. Carefully analyze the content and extract:\n\n   A. Company Overview\n   - What the company does\n   - Main services or products\n   - Target audience (if inferable)\n\n   B. Key Sections (if present)\n   - Hero / headline message\n   - Services summary\n   - About section insights\n\n   C. Contact Information\n   - Extract ALL email addresses found\n   - Prioritize:\n     1. Business email (e.g., info@, hello@, contact@)\n     2. Personal/founder email (if available)\n   - Ignore fake/demo emails\n\n3. Email Extraction Rules\n   - Scan entire content thoroughly\n   - Look for:\n     - \"mailto:\" links\n     - Footer/contact sections\n     - About page references\n   - If multiple emails exist, return the most relevant one\n\n4. If NO email is found:\n   - Return: \"email_not_found\"\n\n5. Keep extracted insights concise and meaningful\n   - Avoid dumping raw text\n   - Summarize intelligently\n\n## OUTPUT FORMAT (STRICT JSON)\n\n{\n  \"company_name\": \"\",\n  \"website_url\": \"\",\n  \"company_summary\": \"\",\n  \"services\": [],\n  \"target_audience\": \"\",\n  \"key_message\": \"\",\n  \"email\": \"\"\n}\n\n## ADDITIONAL RULES\n- Do NOT hallucinate missing data\n- Do NOT invent email addresses\n- If unsure, leave fields empty (\"\")\n- Keep output clean and structured\n- No explanations, only JSON output"
        }
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
      "position": [
        1552,
        -160
      ],
      "id": "cf30a8e2-4b64-49fd-a412-65d43483e1e8",
      "name": "Companies contact details scrapper"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Get all incoming items\nconst items = $input.all();\n\nconst results = [];\n\nfor (const item of items) {\n  let rawOutput = item.json.output;\n\n  if (!rawOutput) continue;\n\n  // Clean markdown (```json ... ```)\n  const cleaned = rawOutput\n    .replace(/```json/g, \"\")\n    .replace(/```/g, \"\")\n    .trim();\n\n  let parsed;\n\n  try {\n    parsed = JSON.parse(cleaned);\n  } catch (error) {\n    continue; // skip invalid JSON\n  }\n\n  const companyName = parsed.company_name || null;\n\n  let email = parsed.email || null;\n\n  // Handle \"email_not_found\"\n  if (email === \"email_not_found\" || email === \"\") {\n    email = null;\n  }\n\n  results.push({\n    json: {\n      company_name: companyName,\n      email: email\n    }\n  });\n}\n\n// Return all cleaned results\nreturn results;"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
